{"tid":2242752,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"18歲男生藏面罩噴漆 准撤控守行為兩年","createTime":"2020-10-14T08:43:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T09:28:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"30f9f4de0513ed87578e9fc7b7539452e909622a","tid":2242752,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T08:43:01.000Z","msg":"網民去年11月12日發起「破曉行動」，示威者響應網上號召堵路，警方在大埔驅散黑衣人時，拘捕兩名男生及一名廚師，分別在三人身上發現士巴拿、噴漆等物品。案件今在粉嶺法院再訊，藏有噴漆的男生原被控管有任何物品意圖摧毀或損壞財產罪，今獲控方撤控，裁判官批准男生以2,000元簽保守行為兩年結案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201014/PQSOWCLPJBBRBCA55FJOQD3GPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201014%2FPQSOWCLPJBBRBCA55FJOQD3GPY%2F&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2vMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=e57176ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201014%2FPQSOWCLPJBBRBCA55FJOQD3GPY%2F&h=725c6775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201014/PQSOWCLPJBBRBCA55FJOQD3GPY/</a>"},{"pid":"7a7787b0c5f6124748ca4b680c30207ccdd1ff04","tid":2242752,"uid":318952,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T08:52:09.000Z","msg":"良官一生平安"},{"pid":"7e90e2b8c5cf423ef2d83902aa8e1017ed03b065","tid":2242752,"uid":89641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:04:46.000Z","msg":"律政屍又上訴架啦, 反正次次都排個紅官加刑"},{"pid":"36d2475866363ebf6acabc68bf6f9771b11ac142","tid":2242752,"uid":177168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:05:37.000Z","msg":"快啲離開香港<br />\n小心department of joke 玩嘢"},{"pid":"3110f252763c110ee3bf1a3822f13b55fc9d631d","tid":2242752,"uid":45635,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7e90e2b8c5cf423ef2d83902aa8e1017ed03b065","tid":2242752,"uid":89641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:04:46.000Z","msg":"律政屍又上訴架啦, 反正次次都排個紅官加刑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:06:00.000Z","msg":"今次係控方撤控<img src=\"/as